snippet.textDisplay:
I'm at home right now listening to Sanam Marvi and Samhin Johar -- with tears welling up in my eyes -- because both singers have such a soulful voice.
Khol Khol Kaaljat penetrates the heart - Today this song has been singled at least 50 times in Mumbai's local metro. Baba Bullesah's philosophy of living life is amazing - Sufi music is the soul of our India and Pakistan - It brings people closer as human beings - I think that there is a flame of love, harmony and equality in the hearts of people.. It is because of Faiz Ahmed Sahab that he knows how much people love him
